c: 3
v: 167
t: "u ad Iรฉeรด anwi ay d ixabiten. Nnan asen: \"yyaw, nna$et deg ubrid n ร–ebbi, ne$ รฉedmet\". Nnan: \"lemmer nessin a nenna$, yili nedda n yidwen\". Assen, nitni, ar tijehli, ne$ $eรด liman, ay qeรดben kteรด. Qqaren, s yimawen nnsen, ayen ur nelli deg ulawen nnsen. ร–ebbi Yif akw akken Iรฉรดa ayen teffren"